game.name: Super Barbie Wedding Fashion
game.description:
Wow! The beautiful Barbie is going to tie the knot with her handsome love Ken today. Isla and Delancy will be her bridesmaids who would help the girl to enjoy the celebration of her special day. Not only wedding girl, but her bridesmaids also want to look fabulous on that day. Your cool fashionable abilities have encouraged them to hire you as their personal stylist. Will you accept this offer right away? Join Super Barbie Wedding Fashion game today and help three girls to get a wonderful wedding look! 

You have to put your designer abilities to challenge to help the sweet couple to enjoy the endless happiness. It is now in your hands to make Super Barbie look special on her marriage in this brand new dressing game for girls. Browse through wider outfit collection to help girl to become the most fashionable bride! Start with the wedding girl and then move to change the overall look of her bridesmaid by applying your unique dress skill!

It is a special day for Super Barbie, so try to mix and match as many items as you can to give your girl a nice wedding style. Give her a perfect while color gown, a purple color or a blue and purple dress as per your choice in this html5 princess game! Do not forget to adorn her with a matching jewelry to complete her look. Hurry up! The other girls are also waiting for their turn. Select the suitable outfits to allow them enjoy this precious day with her!
